8 B. The purpose of the database shall be to do all of the following:
9 (1) Improve transparency in medical reimbursement trends.
10 (2) Assist in enforcement and maintenance of an appropriate fee
11 schedule.
12 (3) Evaluate medical utilization patterns and outcomes.
13 (4) Detect fraud, waste, and abuse.
14 (5) Support policy development, rate analysis, and system oversight.
