24 analyze, and report professional and technical claims charge and payment data
25 for actuarial review and system oversight purposes. The submitted data shall
26 be utilized to develop evidence-based fee schedule recommendations to the office
27 and to identify system imbalances, including:
28 (a) Outlier provider claims patterns.
29 (b) Unpaid claims.
30 (c) Underpaid claims.
